1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, shared and protected when you interact with Chat GPT Chat Bot, a Discord bot powered by the ChatGPT API. By using this bot, you agree to the practices described in this policy.

2. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information:

Interaction Data: The messages you send to the bot, the commands you use, and the responses generated by the bot.
Technical Data: Your Discord user ID, your Discord server, and other technical information necessary for the bot to function.
3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect to:

Improve the Bot: Analyze interactions to improve bot responses and identify technical issues.
Personalize the Experience: Tailor bot responses to your preferences and interaction history.
Ensure Security: Detect and prevent abuse, spam, and other malicious activities.
Comply with Legal Obligations: Respond to legal requests and comply with applicable regulations.
4. Sharing Your Information

We do not share your personal information with third parties, except in the following circumstances:   

Service Providers: We may share anonymized data with third-party service providers (e.g., hosting providers) to ensure the bot's operation.   
Legal Compliance: We may disclose your information if required by law or to respond to a lawful request from a public authority.
5. Data Security

We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure or destruction.   

6. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access Your Data: Request a copy of the data we hold about you.   
Rectify Your Data: Request the correction of any inaccurate data.
Erase Your Data: Request the deletion of your data.
Restrict Processing: Request the restriction of processing your data in certain circumstances.
Object to Processing: Object to the processing of your data on legitimate grounds.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the new policy on our website or through the bot.   

8. Contact

For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at help.chatgpt.discordbot@gmail.com.

Key points to remember:

Transparency: Clearly explain what data is collected and why.
Security: Assure users that their data is protected.
Compliance: Adhere to applicable regulations, such as GDPR.
User Rights: Inform users of their rights regarding their data.
